Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to ProSeka AfterTalk for the "Beyond the Unraveled Threads" event! I'm Rina Honnizumi, the voice of Shizuku Hinomori from MORE MORE JUMP!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In this ProSeka AfterTalk, we'll look back on the event story and enjoy the AfterLive together with everyone watching the stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This edition covers the "Beyond the Unraveled Threads" event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The event just finished a moment ago. Everyone, how did you like the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have so many things I want to talk about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it incredible?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So much happened, and I'm planning to dive deep into all of that today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll stick around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:11:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, please post your thoughts on the event or this broadcast using the hashtag #ProSekaAfterTalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The staff has set up the YouTube chat so I can see it right here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'll be picking up your comments as we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the management team has provided me with a device today,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'll use it to look at the story and the illustrations of the featured members with all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For today's AfterLive, I'll be operating the device myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm planning to join the same room as you all to watch the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, right before the AfterLive starts, I'll create a Room ID...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll set it up so we can all enter at the same time, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure some of you might need to switch devices or get things ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'd be very happy if you could start preparing for that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's jump right into looking back at the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's review the story for "Beyond the Unraveled Threads."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see everyone in the comments saying things like "the entertainment industry is terrifying."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.16,0:12:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I think the way Shizuku faced her own past was just so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt this when I first read the script too, but it really depicts the realistic behind-the-scenes side of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There were quite a few painful scenes, but Shizuku...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she faced those things head-on without running away, we got that kind of ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing how the story concluded, I just really want to tell Shizuku she did a great job.
Comment: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary - review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to say thank you to the members of MORE MORE JUMP!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk more about the deeper details a bit later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.44,0:13:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to watch one episode here with everyone today. Which one do you want to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, I want to see the intense battle during the actual I-Haza performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe episode 7 or 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you all think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had bits and pieces of Shizuku's past from her Cheerful Days era before,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but this time we really got to dig deep into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It really felt like we saw exactly what happened back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm torn, but it looks like most people are saying episode 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Episode 7?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone okay with 7?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's watch episode 7 together, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Watching it with all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,makes it so much more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Episode 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.00,0:27:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.40,0:27:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see people in the YouTube chat saying it made them cry or sending applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.00,0:27:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.76,0:28:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.84,0:28:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.16,0:28:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to head off soon to get ready for the next part.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.12,0:28:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll keep my thoughts brief for now,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.60,0:28:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.96,0:28:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing Shizuku's past like this, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.76,0:28:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shizuku is just such a kind person.
Comment: 0,0:28:26.36,0:28:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary - review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.36,0:28:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The strength she showed by having her own will and being able to say "thank you" face-to-face...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.80,0:28:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That really stood out to me in this scene. Now that I'm putting it into words,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.78,0:28:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and especially since it was during the actual shoot, Shizuku having the courage to clearly express her feelings and everything she wanted to say makes her the coolest in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.02,0:28:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I really just want to give her a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.06,0:29:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In my heart, I'm already hugging her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.56,0:29:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She's truly the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.68,0:29:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And since Shizuku doesn't get angry, Airi-chan steps in and gets all feisty for her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.88,0:29:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That dynamic is just so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.52,0:29:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It captures that intense idol atmosphere, and Airi-chan's role in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.00,0:29:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I have some thoughts on that too, so I'd like to talk about that a bit more in the second half.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.32,0:48:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.38,0:48:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so nice being able to watch this together with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.56,0:48:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.08,0:48:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart is just pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.17,0:48:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.32,0:48:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.18,0:48:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That was our new song.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.08,0:48:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the new song we briefly introduced on the last Wandasho Channel, and it looked so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.24,0:49:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Momojan has performed many different songs up until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.62,0:49:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and I felt like we were able to show many different sides and expressions each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.48,0:49:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But this showed a different kind of coolness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.92,0:49:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Since this was an AfterLive, seeing it as a live performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.36,0:49:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,combined with the outfits, it was just incredibly cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.44,0:49:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The way the lighting looked when Len-kun came to the center during the transition to the pre-chorus... I really loved that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.06,0:49:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was truly great. And those high notes... The recording was so much fun too.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.44,0:50:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When it came to the recording, since the theme of this story was about Shizuku taking that next step forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.46,0:50:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like Shizuku was gaining her wings, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.76,0:50:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like this song had the power to capture that sense of awakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.40,0:50:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first received the materials, so many feelings were packed into the lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.40,0:50:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I really wanted to...
Comment: 0,0:50:24.60,0:50:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary - review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.60,0:50:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to express everything I felt... What we just showed you was the game-size version,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.08,0:50:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but I hope there'll be a chance to share the full version with you all somewhere, someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.56,0:50:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When that time comes, please do listen to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.04,0:50:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I put it? That feeling of Shizuku taking flight after the second chorus...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.44,0:50:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be so happy if you could really feel that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.64,0:50:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's saying they want to hear the full version!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.20,0:51:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But even in this version,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.92,0:51:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that feeling of "I'm not afraid of anything anymore" at the end of the chorus really reached everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.60,0:51:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.86,0:51:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And then after that, everyone waves their hands and the stage suddenly brightens up... I really love that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.96,0:51:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.48,0:51:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.00,0:51:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, thank you all so much for getting hyped up with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.08,0:51:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This 3DMV was also uploaded to the official ProSeka YouTube channel today at 10:10 PM...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.28,0:51:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.52,0:51:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already up, so please go check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.76,0:51:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it lots, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.80,0:51:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.64,0:52:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, I'd like for us to take a look at the new illustrations that were added.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.04,0:52:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There are five of them, and the cards were all incredibly cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.00,0:52:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start by looking at Shizuku's.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.59,0:52:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.80,0:52:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.44,0:52:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the trained version.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.32,0:52:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.92,0:52:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the flowers... the big flower Shizuku is sitting on,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.88,0:52:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it has this stained-glass or glass-like feel to it that I really love.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.44,0:52:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It has this beauty that feels both fleeting and fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.04,0:52:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I really feel that from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.94,0:52:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And here is the untrained version.
Comment: 0,0:52:59.84,0:53:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary - review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.84,0:53:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this illustration was the first one released?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.92,0:53:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, look... Arisa-chan was partially visible in the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.64,0:53:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was posted as an image on Twitter and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.24,0:53:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It really makes you wonder,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.04,0:53:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who is this girl?"
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.56,0:53:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at this single illustration, Shizuku has such a cheerful expression,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.16,0:53:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but then Airi-chan is hissing, and Arisa-chan is just like, "Hmph."
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.90,0:53:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really funny. Once you've seen the story, it all makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.96,0:53:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.48,0:53:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I really love this. Arisa-chan is irresistible, and Airi-chan's expression is...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.10,0:53:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just great.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.80,0:53:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is Honoka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.48,0:53:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she super cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.60,0:53:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The trained version...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.24,0:53:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.06,0:54:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a total change from Shizuku's outfit. The black and white with red accents is so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.84,0:54:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And this leaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.40,0:54:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The way she's wearing a leaf on her head is just adorable, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.16,0:54:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I mentioned Korpokkur earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.64,0:54:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but she really has that fairy-like vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.96,0:54:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And here is the untrained version.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.72,0:54:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Snack time!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.00,0:54:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, it's just like that at the ProSeka studio. They always provide delicious food in the waiting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.64,0:54:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone really digs in.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.80,0:54:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a bento today too, and there are snacks laid out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.12,0:54:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually quite realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.16,0:54:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That feeling of being nervous before a show, but the snacks are so good you eat them anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.36,0:54:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just munching away.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.60,0:54:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely want you all to check out this side story.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.38,0:55:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Comment: 0,0:55:00.04,0:55:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary - review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.04,0:55:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.64,0:55:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.64,0:55:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And next is Airi Momoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.66,0:55:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is the trained version.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.32,0:55:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This outfit is similar to the one Honoka was wearing earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.10,0:55:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but the skirt part is slightly different. Airi has flowers spread out like a pannier,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.00,0:55:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's just so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.20,0:55:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.80,0:55:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The droplets scattered around her make it look like the rain just stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.52,0:55:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That feeling really reminds me of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.44,0:55:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And here is the untrained art.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.02,0:55:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This was in the story too, but Airi really is
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.10,0:55:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,always worried about Shizuku Hinomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.40,0:55:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always asking,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.28,0:55:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Are you okay?"
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.72,0:55:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Shizuku tends to keep things to herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.54,0:56:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.04,0:56:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Airi is always there to check on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.28,0:56:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.44,0:56:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Without Airi, the Shizuku we know today wouldn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.56,0:56:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even back in the theater days, Airi encouraged her so much during her time in Q-T,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.70,0:56:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can really see the bond between these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.44,0:56:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we have Haruka Kiritani.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.04,0:56:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The untrained art.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.32,0:56:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.32,0:56:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this little frog getting startled.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.84,0:56:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this expression just the cutest?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.24,0:56:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She's landing right on a leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.00,0:56:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.78,0:56:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka's outfit has a bit of orange mixed with the red, which is also super cute.
Comment: 0,0:56:48.00,0:56:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary - review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.00,0:56:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,These slight differences in the outfits...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.76,0:56:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.74,0:56:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And the flowers are just gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.53,0:56:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.93,0:57:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And next,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.76,0:57:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,here is the untrained art.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.52,0:57:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the actual studio where they film Eye Hazard?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.96,0:57:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The background with the camera, the exit sign in the back...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.88,0:57:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The lighting of the exit sign, and the monitor in the bottom right under the camera...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.42,0:57:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite detailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.60,0:57:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It really captures what it's like to stand in a studio and look at the cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.84,0:57:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Haruka-chan here
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.84,0:57:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,looks a bit nervous. This expression right before going live is so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.88,0:57:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.50,0:57:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But it really does look like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.76,0:57:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They're constantly filming you from all sorts of angles and with different expressions,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.04,0:57:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and then they switch between cameras to create the screen everyone usually sees.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.08,0:57:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.92,0:57:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's incredibly realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.00,0:58:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, we have MEIKO-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.12,0:58:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,MEIKO, you look so elegant!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.84,0:58:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This white... this white outfit is just stunning.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.94,0:58:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It suits her so well. That's our MEIKO.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.72,0:58:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks so mature and wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.82,0:58:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Holding the flowers too.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.72,0:58:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so cute. The way the sleeves flare out a bit is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.04,0:58:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So we've looked through them all. I wanted to write that the group name got cut off,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.40,0:58:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but because of the character limit, it just says "got cut off."
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.92,0:58:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That happens sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.40,0:58:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Comment: 0,0:58:48.08,0:58:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary - review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.08,0:58:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The costumes are so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.96,0:58:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They're quite simple... Oh, right, and about the comments...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.84,0:59:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone pointed this out to me, and looking at Shizuku's outfit, I see it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.38,0:59:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first saw the card illustration, I just thought, "Oh, she's a fairy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.20,0:59:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just looking at it thinking how cute it was, but then...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.14,0:59:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone told me that this might actually be Thumbelina.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.42,0:59:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew the title of Thumbelina, of course, but I'd never actually read the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.00,0:59:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So I looked up what kind of story it was. To summarize, a tiny girl born from a flower is named Thumbelina,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.66,0:59:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and she gets kidnapped and faces all sorts of dangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.88,0:59:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of things happen to her, she really goes through a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.60,0:59:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But at the very end, a swa... swallow?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.90,0:59:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A swallow saves her, and she becomes free. It's a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.39,0:59:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.76,0:59:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, aren't these swallows?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.64,1:00:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The black and white.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.68,1:00:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, Minori, Airi, and Haruka all look like swallows.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.60,1:00:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The yellow on the chest looks like a beak. I think whoever noticed that is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.82,1:00:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for telling me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.92,1:00:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It really makes so much sense when you look at it that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.84,1:00:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It changes your perspective. There's even a frog here, and a frog appears in the story too.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.88,1:00:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In Thumbelina.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.40,1:00:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It really clicked for me. It's so interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.12,1:00:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The story of Thumbelina is about how if you don't give up,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.40,1:00:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,your dreams will come true and you'll be free. I felt like that's exactly what this story is about.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.56,1:00:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,With the swallows' help, Shizuku is able to spread her wings.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.08,1:00:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so MMJ, honestly.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.96,1:00:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is... Thanks for letting me know.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.88,1:00:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.16,1:01:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, combined with the story of "The Thread That Leads to You,"
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.78,1:01:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the illustrations are just wonderful.
Comment: 0,1:01:07.00,1:01:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary - review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.00,1:01:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.04,1:01:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.56,1:01:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I really wanted to talk about Arisa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.12,1:01:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In this story...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.92,1:01:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The structure has her clashing intensely with Shizuku and the other members,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.40,1:01:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so from a certain perspective, Arisa-chan and the former theater girls...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.94,1:01:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,well, they aren't exactly villains, but there were moments where you might think, "Oh, these girls..."
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.00,1:01:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But as MEIKO said, they're all serious about being idols.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.06,1:01:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They truly wanted that center position that Shizuku got,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.12,1:02:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and they've worked incredibly hard for it. That's why they get so seriously jealous,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.82,1:02:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and why they put in so much effort.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.80,1:02:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They were pretty aggressive, but I felt Arisa-chan was a very straightforward person.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.72,1:02:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Shizuku felt that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.48,1:02:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment Shizuku met Arisa-chan and the other theater members,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.26,1:02:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Arisa-chan was basically like, "I'm going all out, so you'd better do the same."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.76,1:02:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the vibe.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.56,1:02:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She really puts those feelings into words and communicates them.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.84,1:02:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.88,1:02:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that straightforwardness, that sense of always facing things with everything she's got, was really cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.88,1:02:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.92,1:02:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I really did.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.50,1:02:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.76,1:03:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.96,1:03:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Things like hiding the costumes did happen,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.84,1:03:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and obviously, the way they went about it wasn't right.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.68,1:03:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.92,1:03:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanting to be the center and having those emotions isn't a bad thing at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.08,1:03:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can totally understand that because they're so serious, those feelings of frustration arise, so I have to treat it as a cautionary tale.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.68,1:03:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like this wasn't just someone else's problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.72,1:03:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you misdirect that jealousy or aim it at the wrong target, really bad things can happen.
Comment: 0,1:03:46.62,1:03:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary - review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.62,1:03:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It is incredibly difficult, but you just have to find a way to resolve those feelings within yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.08,1:04:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Having that competitive spirit can lead to your own motivation,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.08,1:04:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and I personally want to be the kind of person who uses that as energy to work harder.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.62,1:04:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that way quite often myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.36,1:04:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, "She is so good..." and things like that. Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.96,1:04:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Every single day, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.92,1:04:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.74,1:04:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But on the flip side, Shizuku said something she really shouldn't have said to the girls who were seriously aiming for that center position.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.20,1:04:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She ended up blurting it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.40,1:04:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, she didn't mean any harm. I think everyone who knows Shizuku's personality understands that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.20,1:04:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't malicious, but Shizuku was so overwhelmed at the time that she could only see what was right in front of her.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.28,1:04:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She was in a period where she could only focus on herself, so she accidentally said, "I think there are other girls more suited for this center spot."
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.52,1:04:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It just came out.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.42,1:04:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that feeling too.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.80,1:04:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, the pressure of being the center is insane.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.12,1:05:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There are expectations and how you present yourself, and above all, Shizuku wasn't being her true self.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.60,1:05:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She had a persona that she only maintained thanks to everyone else,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.56,1:05:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,which made it even harder.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.20,1:05:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That was part of it too, and honestly,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.36,1:05:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,this whole situation is just so raw.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.56,1:05:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.08,1:05:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,To be so young and sensitive, and then have your worth decided by whether someone else chooses you... that's just cruel.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.14,1:05:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't become the center just by working hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.92,1:05:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tough because you can't get there unless someone else recognizes you and says, "You are the center."
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.06,1:05:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I also feel like that's exactly why these girls are able to shine so brightly.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.24,1:05:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Reading this scenario made me think I should really be careful myself, but because she went through this rough patch,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.48,1:06:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,we have the Shizuku we know today. Without this, Momojan wouldn't have been born.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.62,1:06:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel very grateful for that as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.84,1:06:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shizuku was saying "thank you" too. She was truly, truly grateful.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.34,1:06:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And Arisa-chan... she stuck to her guns right until the very end.
Comment: 0,1:06:17.52,1:06:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary - review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.52,1:06:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And her words weren't wrong at all... though her actions might have been.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.12,1:06:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a single word she said was wrong. In the scenario we just watched,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.70,1:06:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,she was pretty aggressive during the actual recording of I-Haza. You might think,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.32,1:06:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"Why would she say something like that on a TV show?" but in her own way, she understands that I-Haza has viewers who look forward to idols having those deep, pointed conversations, and she does it to liven up the show.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.52,1:07:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She's working with Marina-chan, the MC, and the members of Cheerful*Days on the panel to make it exciting, so you can really feel her level of commitment.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.34,1:07:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a true professional.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.66,1:07:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.40,1:07:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It does make you nervous, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.96,1:07:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really on edge too, wondering what was going to happen,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.44,1:07:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but she's not a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.06,1:07:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just very straightforward, serious, and strict with both herself and others.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.48,1:07:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I really wanted to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.68,1:07:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I ended up rambling quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.04,1:07:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.84,1:07:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I really felt that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.96,1:07:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.20,1:07:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.48,1:07:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're working hard, your perspective becomes subjective.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.10,1:07:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only see what's right in front of you. In times like that, it'd be great if you could fly a drone camera way up high and get a wider, bird's-eye view of things.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.58,1:07:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that, then even in moments where you're wondering "Why?"...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.50,1:08:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can both understand that the other person had their own position, or their own feelings, or that things happened while you weren't looking, then I'm sure you can reach an understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.60,1:08:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it would help with communication too, so it's a really great lesson for daily life.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.43,1:08:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.14,1:08:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.60,1:08:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,what I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.12,1:08:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This story was another turning point where Shizuku
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.88,1:08:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,took a step forward. We really got to see Shizuku's purity, her strength,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.60,1:08:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and just how cool she can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.85,1:08:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.92,1:08:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The title is "Beyond the Untangled Threads," and it uses the word "threads."
Comment: 0,1:08:44.56,1:08:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary - review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.56,1:08:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The word "thread" is even in the lyrics of "Metamoren Ribbon."
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.76,1:08:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a key term, and I really love these little connections.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.27,1:08:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.96,1:09:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure everyone has their own thoughts and opinions, so please use the hashtag to tweet about it. It's a very raw story, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.96,1:09:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the characters people empathize with will vary completely,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.08,1:09:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's only natural to have different feelings. I hope you all share those with each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.92,1:09:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It really was a fascinating scenario.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.28,1:09:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.24,1:09:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I'm being so serious, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.21,1:09:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.52,1:09:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually surprising myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.32,1:09:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since I'm alone today and the story was what it was, I wanted to make sure I said what I needed to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.60,1:09:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have moments like this too.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.92,1:09:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I often host the Wandasho Channel and things like that, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.16,1:09:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first appeared on screen alone, I bet there was a moment where everyone thought,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.36,1:09:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Wait, is this going to be okay?"
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.52,1:10:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But I do have my serious moments too.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.40,1:10:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, thanks for sticking with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.28,1:10:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.20,1:10:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was only for a short while, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.72,1:10:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This concludes the ProSeka AfterTalk for "Beyond the Tangled Threads."
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.44,1:10:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you to everyone watching the stream.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.52,1:10:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw all the comments you were sending in.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.56,1:10:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I couldn't address every single one of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.75,1:10:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.88,1:10:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Being able to join the same room for the Live, and connecting with everyone
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.36,1:10:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,watching this stream in real time... it has a different kind of charm than watching alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.16,1:10:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.24,1:10:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it for all of you?
